## Common Troubleshooting Commands

| Command           | Purpose                      |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------- |
| ipconfig          | Displays IP configuration    |
| ipconfig /all     | Shows detailed configuration |
| ipconfig /release | Releases DHCP address        |
| ipconfig /renew   | Requests new IP              |
| ping              | Tests connectivity           |
| tracert           | Shows packet route           |
| nslookup          | Tests DNS                    |
| arp -a            | Displays ARP cache           |
| netstat           | Shows network connections    |
| route print       | Displays routing table       |

Linux alternatives include:

* ifconfig
* ip addr
* ping
* traceroute
* dig
* nslookup
* ip route

